The,Amazon,Developer,Publishing,API,allows,developers,to,build,new,apps,or,upgrade,existing,ones,This,API,is,restricted,to,developers,with,permission,to,participate,in,the,developer,preview,The,selection,process,involves,filling,out,a,short,questionnaire,Only,successful,developers,are,contacted,with,notification,of,access,details,The,API,sends,JSON,formatted,requests,and,responses